 letterings probably not broken on right, contra Orsi: Seiane! Mnesthei sou ho Theos.-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>39.1028\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Griesheimer\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>153 no.8 ph\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/B29C27GP\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001939\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001939\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Orsi\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1893\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>303 no. 96\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/V7HNHTAG\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.8\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/759ZXHKQ\"/>\n                        \u00